data.description: Beautiful bungalow home perfectly situated on a large, private lot with large, mature trees and privacy fencing in the backyard. This home welcomes you with tons of windows and natural light, gorgeous wood floors, 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Beautiful wood flooring flows through the home as you are met with the charm of glass french doors and the a kitchen swinging door. Outside you will find a large yard, back deck and a 3 car garage with an office or workshop. Bring your ideas and make it your own! Relax on the front porch or enjoy the back yard or take a short walk to the shopping and restaurants and year-round events that await downtown! Easy access to I-85 as well! This home is turn key and move in ready!
